meaning_str.bing:
v. 拉；拉动；拖；吸引
n. 拉；吸引力；拽；扯
网络. 拔；拉动式；拉力

拉；拔出；抽出；拖；吸引；扯；拽；（使车辆）转向；打斜；扳动；拉上；取消；撤销（活动、广告等）；拉伤；划；扭转；（耍手腕）得逞；吃力地运转；将…拖在身后；吸引异性
拉；拉力；牵引力；吸引力；影响力；诱惑；深吸；艰难攀登；一满口（或大口）饮料；一次努力尝试；吸引人的特质；牵引用的工具

1.en: "I'll pull out the laptop, and when I'm on Michigan Avenue here in Chicago, put it on a garbage can or on the seat of a bus stop, " he said.
1.cn: 在芝加哥这里的密歇根大街时，我会掏出笔记本，把它放在垃圾桶上或公交车站的座位上。

2.en: Even with a flurry of online traffic, retailers appeared to pull off Cyber Monday without a glitch.
2.cn: 不过零售商们还是经受住了在线星期一的流量冲击。

3.en: This will give you a warning and a little bit of time to pull out your secondary and prepare for a firefight.
3.cn: 这会给你换成备用武器并准备火拼的一点警告与时间。

0.en: Pull my finger. My hand is messed up.
0.cn: 拉我的手指，我的手毁了。

1.en: Pull your pants up, Patrick. We're going home.
1.cn: 把你的裤子拉上去，派崔克。我们回家了。

2.en: Ready. Steady. Go. Come on, boys. Come on, pull. Come on, the girls, pull. I am pulling.
2.cn: 准备！预备！开始！男生，加油。努力，拉。女生，加油。我在拉呀。

3.en: Come on. Just give me your hand, I'll pull you back over.

4.en: I will tie the sack onto the chain here, pull one of the two strings behind you and the sack should disappear up to the top floor.
4.cn: 我要把袋子口绑在链子上，你身后有两条绳子，拉一条袋子就被拉上去了。

5.en: You did not pull it up. I have to be there in an hour. I'm the best man.
5.cn: 那叫拉上拉链吗？我一个小时就得赶到，我是伴郎。

6.en: Could you pull the curtains open for me? The astronauts from the space shuttle are gonna be on the news.
6.cn: 你帮我把窗帘拉起来好吗？太空人会上电视新闻。

7.en: You don't understand. If we go back, they'll swamp the boat. They'll pull us right down, I'm telling you.
7.cn: 你不明白，我们回去，船会被挤翻，我们会被拉下去。

8.en: What you're going to do is you're going to stick your thumb down its throat, grab the guts and pull.
8.cn: 你现在要做的是把你的手指伸进它的喉咙，抓住内脏，往外拉。

9.en: Let's pull the crackers. There are paper hats inside. And party trumpets. And jokes. What wobbles in the sky? I don't know. A jetlicopter.
9.cn: 我们来拉圣诞拉炮吧。你们看哪，这里面有一顶纸帽子。还有派对喇叭。还有一个笑话，什么东西在天空中晃荡？这个我不知道。一架直升机。

10.en: Let's pull the crackers. There are paper hats inside. And party trumpets. And jokes. What wobbles in the sky? I don't know. A jetlicopter.
10.cn: 我们来拉圣诞拉炮吧。你们看哪，这里面有一顶纸帽子。还有派对喇叭。还有一个笑话，什么东西在天空中晃荡？这个我不知道。一架直升机。

11.en: If you don't like him, just pull me aside after 20 minutes, and say he's not for you, and we'll keep looking.
11.cn: 如果你不喜欢他，20分钟后，拉我到一边说他不适合你，我们就接着找。

12.en: Hello, Mr. Pig speaking. It's Daddy. Oh, hello. I'm stuck. Hello Daddy. Hang on, we'll pull you out. One. Two. Three. Pull. Daddy is a blackberry bush.
12.cn: 你好，我是猪爸爸。是爸爸。哦，你好，我卡住了。爸爸，你好。等一下，我们来你出来。一、二、三，拉！爸爸变成黑莓丛了。哈哈哈。

13.en: You'll pull me back out, won't you? Or Clementine will make sure neither of us makes it back. Now. Please.
13.cn: 你会把我拉回来的，对吧？否则克莱门汀会让我们两个都回不去，开始吧，拜托了。

14.en: All right fine. Fine, I'll do it. I've just got to get this off the screen. Carol and Susan are still upset that you taught him pull my finger.
14.cn: 好吧，让我来，我们得把这个消掉，卡萝还在气你教他“拉我的手指”。

15.en: Sameen risked everything at the Stock Exchange, not just to save our lives, but to pull the whole world back from the brink of disaster.
15.cn: 萨姆恩在证交所付出了一切，不仅救了我们的命，还把整个世界从灾难边缘拉回来。

16.en: It's not funny! Well, it does look a bit funny. We'll have to pull you out. Peppa's friends are helping to free her. Hurray!
16.cn: 这一点都不好笑！看上去确实有点好笑。我们必须把你拉出来。佩奇的朋友们都来帮忙了。好嘞。

17.en: Then simply sit, spin, stand, stretch. Maybe unloosen your pants. And step, grab, tiny pivot, pull, and you're there.
17.cn: 然后坐下，旋转，站起，跨一大步……也许要把裤子松一松。然后……并腿，抓床，略微转身，用力一拉，到了。

18.en: Well, that seems simple enough. Point bag away from home, feet firmly on ground, pull string, releasing the winds. All right, let's do it for real.
18.cn: 看上去很简单吗。把袋子指向家的反方向，站稳了，拉绳子把风放出来。好的，来做一遍吧。

19.en: Boys are against girls. When I say go, you must pull the rope with all your strength. The girls will win. No, they won't. The boys will win.
19.cn: 男女大对抗。听到我说开始以后，你们就使劲拉绳子。女生会赢的。你们不会赢，我们男生会赢。
